      "htmlContent": "<div class=\"comp-41-button-container\"><button class=\"Btn\"> Pay <svg class=\"svgIcon\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\"><path d=\"M512 80c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16v32H48V96c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16H512zm16 144V416c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16H64c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V224H528zM64 32C28.7 32 0 60.7 0 96V416c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64H512c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V96c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H64zm56 304c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24s10.7 24 24 24h48c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24H120zm128 0c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24s10.7 24 24 24H360c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24H248z\"></path></svg></button></div>",
